## Cleaner Module - English
cleaner-service-enabled = ✅ Service message cleaning enabled! Join/leave and other service messages will be auto-deleted.
cleaner-service-disabled = ❌ Service message cleaning disabled.
cleaner-bluetext-enabled = ✅ Blue text cleaning enabled! Unrecognized bot commands will be deleted.
cleaner-bluetext-disabled = ❌ Blue text cleaning disabled.
cleaner-need-admin = ❌ You need to be an admin to use this command.
